author: Play On Tabletop
description:
Deadly Print Studios and their amazing effects sponsored this episode.  https://deadlyprintstudio.com The effects for the Votann make that army pop even more! 

Space Marine Steve, a full-time educator, was super busy for a few months but now he is back! It's been too long!  He's here playing his classic Crimson Fist Force and it looks ready to take on Jt and so many Dwarves!  The Votann have brought all the railguns to this fight but will it be enough?
